=\r\nhings like removing possession are specializations. These do not fall under=\r\n the ambit of normal sadhana. Unless one knows well what one is getting int=\r\no, any sadhaka with even basic common sense would do best to stay away. Eve=\r\nry action has its repercussion and one must know well how to\n handle the sa=\r\nme too. Again\n if a spirit is removed by force before the time till which, =\r\nbased on previous karma, it was supposed to be in possession of the individ=\r\nual, then that too starts a new karmic chain which will involve \n(Message over 64 KB, truncated)"}}